msgstr ""
"``GET /api/torrent/top/ips`` — top pairs. ``?limit=`` ``?seed_only=1`` "
"``?days=7|30|90`` (fenêtre) ``?format=csv``."

#: ../../features.rst:433 b7240bc7692748a89aa2a378855ef251
