#: ../../features.rst:437 0411dbf0e48d4c3eaa677ea35b169a3e
msgid ""
"``GET /api/torrent/ip/<ip>/timeline`` — daily counts, last N days "
"(default 30)."
msgstr ""
"``GET /api/torrent/ip/<ip>/timeline`` — compteurs quotidiens sur les N "
"derniers jours (défaut 30)."

#: ../../features.rst:438 a86996ff13d24dda99889a1f579c9504
msgid ""
"``GET /api/torrent/asn/<asn>`` — IPs + torrents for the AS. "
"``?format=csv``."
msgstr "``GET /api/torrent/asn/<asn>`` — IPs + torrents de l'AS. ``?format=csv``."

#: ../../features.rst:440 b091e8a7d6dc4f1a9ea8781dd3be004e
msgid "Write endpoint (admin session or API key):"
msgstr "Endpoint d'écriture (session admin ou clé API) :"

#: ../../features.rst:442 808dc78186164a32b035ebbac408e1f7
msgid ""
"``POST /api/torrent/refresh/<infohash>`` — queue a live rescan. Returns "
"``202 Accepted`` immediately; the scan runs in a background thread. "
"Recorded in the audit log (``torrent_refresh``)."
msgstr ""
"``POST /api/torrent/refresh/<infohash>`` — met en file un rescan à la "
"demande. Retourne ``202 Accepted`` immédiatement ; le scan tourne dans un"
" thread d'arrière-plan. Consigné dans l'audit log (``torrent_refresh``)."

#: ../../features.rst:447 01e09f40e01a4da0b83553d7932ef87a
msgid "Peer IP enrichment"
msgstr "Enrichissement des IP de peers"

#: ../../features.rst:449 ecf2d64a8a014a8f819f86f4e4745eee
msgid ""
"Each peer IP observed during a scan is enriched via `CIRCL "
"<https://www.circl.lu/>`_ services:"
msgstr ""
"Chaque IP de peer observée pendant un scan est enrichie via les services "
"`CIRCL <https://www.circl.lu/>`_ :"

#: ../../features.rst:452 01a639cb782c4e35b77319282f67e1fd
msgid "**ASN** — queried from `IP ASN History <https://ipasnhistory.circl.lu/>`_."
msgstr ""
"**ASN** — récupéré depuis `IP ASN History "
"<https://ipasnhistory.circl.lu/>`_."

#: ../../features.rst:453 294ac2e425214b61a7a7cf09e0b3755d
msgid ""
"**Organisation and country code** — queried from `BGP Ranking <https"
"://bgpranking-ng.circl.lu/>`_."
msgstr ""
"**Organisation et code pays** — récupérés depuis `BGP Ranking <https"
"://bgpranking-ng.circl.lu/>`_."

#: ../../features.rst:455 270937db505f4fc6bf89cb971ecd20fc
msgid "**Reverse DNS** — resolved locally, with a 2-second timeout."
msgstr "**Reverse DNS** — résolu localement, avec un timeout de 2 secondes."

#: ../../features.rst:457 a383e9a5d6414cb1877cb434846d3f3d
msgid ""
"Records are cached in ``DB_TORRENT_HEALTH`` under ``ipenrich:<ip>`` with "
"a TTL governed by ``torrent_health.ip_cache_ttl_days`` in the config "
"(default 7 days; ``0`` disables the TTL)."
msgstr ""
"Les enregistrements sont cachés dans ``DB_TORRENT_HEALTH`` sous "
"``ipenrich:<ip>`` avec un TTL piloté par "
"``torrent_health.ip_cache_ttl_days`` dans la config (défaut 7 jours ; "
"``0`` désactive le TTL)."

#: ../../features.rst:461 877208bc31b34168a8a85770a66c6eae
msgid ""
"Two endpoints expose the enrichment (same auth model as above — admin "
"session or API key):"
msgstr ""
"Deux endpoints exposent l'enrichissement (même modèle d'authentification "
"que ci-dessus — session admin ou clé d'API) :"

#: ../../features.rst:464 0b72ef2f1d1240999ae51e42ca3a0f7b
msgid ""
"``GET /api/enrich/ip/<ip>`` — single IP, optional ``?force=1`` bypass "
"cache."
msgstr ""
"``GET /api/enrich/ip/<ip>`` — IP unique, ``?force=1`` optionnel pour "
"bypass le cache."

#: ../../features.rst:465 8ba32c68704c4f83a1b186ef09d9f489
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"``POST /api/enrich/ip/bulk`` — batch up to 200 IPs per request (JSON "
"``{\"ips\": [...]}`` ). Used by the admin UI to enrich every peer of the "
"displayed scan in one round-trip."
msgstr ""
"``POST /api/enrich/ip/bulk`` — batch jusqu'à 200 IP par requête (JSON "
"``{\"ips\": [...]}`` ). Utilisé par l'UI admin pour enrichir tous les "
"peers d'un scan en un seul aller-retour."

#: ../../features.rst:469 81b841e2da354c37a2d456ac874c699d
msgid "Enrichment runs in two complementary modes:"
msgstr "L'enrichissement fonctionne selon deux modes complémentaires :"

#: ../../features.rst:471 c766bd65540b4eeb8a6721b9512d580e
msgid ""
"**Lazy (default)** — the admin detail page fetches the bulk endpoint at "
"page load; uncached IPs hit CIRCL on demand."
msgstr ""
"**Lazy (par défaut)** — la page de détail admin appelle l'endpoint bulk "
"au chargement ; les IP non cachées atteignent CIRCL à la demande."

#: ../../features.rst:473 3bcf654f945a4b038dcab6b219b0e6ae
msgid ""
"**Proactive (optional)** — ``poetry run enrich-ips`` (cron job, typically"
" daily) walks every stored peer IP and refreshes the cache so the UI is "
"always instant."
msgstr ""
"**Proactif (optionnel)** — ``poetry run enrich-ips`` (cron, typiquement "
"quotidien) parcourt chaque IP de peer stockée et rafraîchit le cache pour"
" que l'UI soit toujours instantanée."

